for any method that involves controller input, going to need an array of size 5 that contains only 0s and 1s
  -each element represents a button that will be active (1) or unactive (0)
  -[up,right,down,left,center]
  
methods that will need this:
  -throwing die
  -general movement on board
  -answering questions (general)
  -special question types (tbd if we implement this)
